data.description: This home has such a welcoming feel with amazing natural light and an open floor plan that is well suited for main level living. Located in a friendly cul de sac and inviting neighborhood. It's a stones throw away from outdoor recreation- Lake Minnequa, gorgeous parks, and trails to explore. The main bedroom features a private bath, huge walk-in closet, secondary closet and a walkout to a quaint sitting area as well as rear yard and detached 2 car garage. This home has been loved and well maintained which is evident upon entering the front door. The eat-in kitchen features plenty of counter space and cabinets. The spotless and shining vinyl linoleum in the kitchen and bath are amazing you'll swear they're real hardwoods. The evaporative cooler just adds another level of comfort for those warm sunny days. And the 2 car detached garage is the icing on the cake. Well worth taking a look see...no disappointments here.
